name: Tiles Splice HEN #2
description:
Generative art is created by a system that operates semi-autonomously with the artist. The artist creates the system and establishes parameters that affect the outcome, but the outcome itself emerges from the system rather than from the artist. Generative art systems are defining the frequency of human/computer symbiotic existence resulting in mathematically calculated artwork. 

Owning one of the tiles is an invitation to join this digital art experiment which will grow and evolve into a Metaverse community of generative art lovers.

Tile: 8192 x 8192 pixels
